{
  "_description": "Effect type definitions - what properties can be modified by effects",
  "_notes": [
    "This file defines valid effect TYPE keywords",
    "Actual named effects (poison, drunk, performance-high, etc.) are in game-data/effects/",
    "Each effect type specifies what game property it modifies",
    "Category determines what kind of modifiers are allowed:",
    "  - stat: Only instant modifiers (STR, DEX, CON, INT, WIS, CHA)",
    "  - capacity: Only instant modifiers (max_hp, max_mana, weight_capacity)",
    "  - resource: Both instant AND periodic modifiers (hp, mana, hunger, fatigue)"
  ],

